			<description><![CDATA[The Indian Air Force has officially released the results for the AFCAT 2026 exam, allowing candidates to check their scores online. This recruitment drive aims to fill 340 positions across various branches. Candidates can find detailed instructions on how to access their scorecards and learn about the next steps, including the crucial interview process conducted by the Air Force Selection Board. Those who meet the cutoff will be shortlisted for further evaluation. Discover all the essential details in this article.]]></description>
