			<description><![CDATA[The Government of India has launched the recruitment process for Multi-Tasking Staff (MTS) positions under the Animal Welfare Board of India. Eligible candidates who have completed their 10th grade can apply offline within 60 days of the advertisement. With three vacancies available and a salary range of ₹18,000 to ₹56,900, this is a significant opportunity for job seekers. Interested applicants should ensure their applications are complete and submitted on time to avoid rejection. For more details, including the application process, visit the official website.]]></description>
