  <p></p> 
  <br> 
  <p></p> 
  <li>Last date for first phase registration – March 15, 2026</li> 
  <p></p> 
  <br> 
  <p></p> 
  <li>Option filling period – March 11 to 16, 2026</li> 
  <p></p> 
  <br> 
  <p></p> 
  <li>Seat allocation process – March 17, 2026</li> 
  <p></p> 
  <br> 
  <p></p>
 </ul>
 <p></p>
 <br>
 <h2>Seat Allocation Results to be Announced in March 2026</h2>
 <p></p>
 <ul> 
  <p></p> 
  <br> 
  <p></p> 
  <li>Reporting period at allocated college – March 19 to 25, 2026</li> 
  <p></p> 
  <br> 
  <p></p> 
  <li>Release date for second phase application forms – March 28, 2026</li> 
  <p></p> 
  <br> 
  <p></p> 
