  <p></p> 
  <br> 
  <p></p> 
  <li>Pay the registration fee</li> 
  <p></p> 
  <br> 
  <p></p> 
  <li>Download and print the confirmation page for future reference.</li> 
  <p></p> 
  <br> 
  <p></p>
 </ol>
 <p></p>
 <br>
 <p></p>
 <p>To apply online, candidates should prepare their name, parent’s name, NEET SS application number, roll number, score, date of birth, category, and citizenship details. For more information, please visit the official website.</p>
