 <p>Submit your application to the Central Bank of India, Regional Office, 7, Civil Lines, University Road, Sagar, Madhya Pradesh, Narsinghpur.</p>
 <br>
 <p>Candidates selected for the interview will be contacted by the bank. This recruitment aims to fill one Attendant and one Watchman position. Regularly check the Central Bank of India's official website for updates.</p>
