			<guid>https://naukrinama.com/government-jobs/punjab-police-recruitment-apply-for-constable-positions-now/cid18349633.htm</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[The Punjab Police Department has announced recruitment for constable positions in both District Police and Armed Police. Applications are open from March 10 to March 30, 2026, exclusively online. Candidates must have completed 12th grade and meet age requirements. The application fee varies by category, and the selection process includes a Computer-Based Test followed by physical and medical evaluations. This is a great opportunity for those seeking a career in law enforcement.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<img src="https://naukrinama.com/static/c1e/client/99589/downloaded/6dd93385d564d333654ea40c20b5f8ae.png" ><h2>Exciting Opportunities in Punjab Police</h2>
 <p><br></p>
 <br>
 <p>Great news for youth aspiring for a role in the police force! The Punjab Police Department has opened applications for constable vacancies in both the District Police and Armed Police divisions. Interested candidates can submit their applications starting today, March 10, 2026, until the closing date of March 30, 2026. Please be aware that only online applications will be accepted; any other submission methods will not be considered.</p>
 <br>
 <h2>Eligibility Criteria</h2>
