  <li>United Arab Emirates</li> 
  <p></p> 
  <br> 
  <p></p>
 </ul>
 <p></p>
 <br>
 <p>This decision was made after a thorough assessment of the current conditions in the region.</p>
 <br>
 <h2>Future Decisions on Exams</h2>
 <p>The CBSE has indicated that any decisions regarding the board exams scheduled after March 16th will be made following a review of the situation on March 14th. This assessment will guide the board in determining the next steps.</p>
 <br>
 <h2>Announcement of New Exam Dates</h2>
 <p>With the postponement of the exams, students are facing additional challenges. The CBSE has assured that it will announce new dates for the postponed examinations in the near future.</p>
