			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<img src="https://naukrinama.com/static/c1e/client/99589/downloaded/8b343d7348b19d39d257216813f4fc22.webp" ><h2>Punjab Police Recruitment Announcement</h2>
 <p></p>
 <div>
  For young individuals dreaming of a government job, there is great news. If you aspire to work in the police department, the Punjab Police has announced vacancies for constables in both the district police and armed police cadre. Eligible candidates can apply for these constable positions from March 10 to March 30, 2026. It is important to note that applications will only be accepted online; no other submission methods will be considered.
 </div>
 <p></p>
 <br>
 <h2>Eligibility Criteria</h2>
 <p></p>
 <div>
