 </div>
 <div>
  - Register for the recruitment on the homepage.
 </div>
 <div>
  - Complete the form by filling in the required details.
 </div>
 <div>
  - Finally, pay the application fee as per your category.
 </div>
 <div>
  - Submit the form and ensure to print a copy for your records.
 </div>
 <p></p>
 <br>
 <h2>Selection Process</h2>
 <p></p>
 <div>
  <b>Selection Procedure</b>
 </div>
 <div>
  The recruitment process will begin with a Common Computer Based Test (CBT). Candidates who pass this exam will be called for the Physical Screening Test (PST), document verification, and medical examination. Those who successfully complete all these stages will have their names included in the final selection list.
